title: Whose comeback was more popular and successful, Stray Kids God's Menu or Ateez Inception? - Quora

response.answer_text: I’d say God’s Menu overall. Inception did amazing internationally, but this comeback just started their increasing recognition in Korea. Stray Kids are pretty solid in Korea (in my opinion), and their comeback was considered one of their most popular comebacks. But then again, this is still very opinionated.
